*Usred* duge zime, boravak u planinama bili je zanimljiv. (In the middle of a long winter, staying in the mountains was interesting.)

*Usred* velikog grada, nijedno drvo nije bilo vidljivo. (In the middle of a big city, no trees were visible.)

*Usredšnjica* je bila obavezna u školama. (The mid-term exam was mandatory in schools.)

*Usredsnošću* je kuća bila izgrađena brže. (With diligence, the house was built faster.)

*Usredšnjavati* obaveze je bilo nepoželjno. (It was undesirable to postpone obligations.)